  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment: 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2). W-AR-02 adversarial sample: multiple credibility factors fall below required levels yet the decision record records Accepted, and assuranceLevel is Medium rather than the High level demanded by COMPOUND-03.",
