    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concludes that the CFD model is accepted for the CPB hemolysis COU. The majority of assessed factors meet required levels, and the overall evidence base is judged sufficient for a Class II device at MRL 2. Shortfalls in software quality assurance, discretization error, output comparison, and model form are noted but deemed acceptable given the medium model influence and the availability of conservative safety margins in the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. No further remediation is required prior to regulatory submission.",
